th bank)===\n\n'''North shore of St. Lawrence River'''\n\n* [[Beaudette River]]\n* [[Delisle River]]\n* [[Rouge River (Vaudreuil-Dorion)|Rouge River]]\n* [[Graisse River]]\n\n===Montreal area===\nSee: [[List of rivers and water bodies of Montreal Island]]\n\n''[[Jesus Island]] ([[Laval, Quebec]]''\n\nNote: No rivers on Jesus Island\n\n''[[Island of Montreal]]''\n* [[Saint Pierre River (Montreal)|Saint Pierre River]]\n* [[Lachine Canal]]\n* [[Canal de l'Aqueduc]]\n* [[Sainte-Anne-de-Bellevue Canal]]\n\n===Watershed of l'Assomption River===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*[[L'Assomption River]]\n**[[l'Achigan River]]\n***[[Jourdain River]]\n***[[Abercromby River]]\n***[[Beauport River (Achigan River tributary)|Beauport River]]\n***[[La Petite Rivi\u00e8re (Achigan River tributary)|La Petite Rivi\u00e8re]]\n**[[Saint-Esprit River]]\n**[[Saint-Georges Brook]]\n**[[Ouareau River]]\n***[[Burton River]]\n***[[Jean-Venne River]]\n****[[Kenny River]]\n***[[Baulne River]]\n***[[Dufresne River]]\n***[[Nord River (Ouareau River tributary)|Nord River]]\n***[[Trudel River]]\n***[[Rouge River (Ouareau River tributary)|Rouge River]]\n****[[Blanche River (Rouge River tributary)|Blanche River]]\n****[[Le Grand Ruisseau (Rouge River tributary)|Le Grand Ruisseau]]\n***[[Saint-Michel River]] (via [[Archambault Lake]]{{dn|date=March 2020}}<!--French WP links to a DAB page with 6 entries-->)\n**[[Noire River (L'Assomption River tributary)|Noire River]]\n***[[Blanche River (Noire River - L'Assomption River tributary)|Blanche River]]\n***[[Leprohon River]]\n***[[Crique \u00e0 David]]\n**[[Rivi\u00e8re de la Boule]]\n**[[Versailles River]]\n**[[Grande rivi\u00e8re Swaggin]]\n***[[Petite rivi\u00e8re Swaggin]]\n**[[McGee River]]\n**[[Lavigne River]]\n**[[Ruisseau du Point du Jour]]\n}}\n\n===North shore of St Lawrence river \u2013 between Repentigny and Trois-Rivi\u00e8res===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*[[Saint-Jean River (Lavaltrie)|Saint-Jean River]]\n**[[Saint-Antoine River (Lavaltrie)|Saint-Antoine River]]\n*[[Saint-Joseph River]]\n*[[Chaloupe River]]\n*[[Bayonne River]]\n**[[Branche de la rivi\u00e8re Bayonne]]\n**[[Berthier River]]\n**[[Bonaventure River (Bayonne River tributary)|Bonaventure River]]\n*[[Chicot River]]\n**[[Sainte-Catherine River]]\n*[[Cach\u00e9e River (D'Autray)]]\n*[[Bois Blanc River]]\n* [[Maskinong\u00e9 River]]\n**[[L'Ormi\u00e8re River]]\n**[[Maskinong\u00e9 Lake]]\n***[[Matambin River]]\n***[[Mastigouche River]]\n****[[Branche \u00e0 Gauche - Mastigouche River]]\n*****[[Rivi\u00e8re du Lac Gauthier]]\n****[[Mastigouche River North]]\n**[[Mandeville River]]\n**[[Blanche River (Maskinong\u00e9 River tributary)]]\n***[[Rouge River (Blanche River - Maskinong\u00e9 River tributary)]]\n*[[Rivi\u00e8re du Loup (Mauricie)|Rivi\u00e8re du Loup]]\n**[[Petite rivi\u00e8re du Loup]]\n**[[Saint-Louis River (Du Loup River tributary)]]\n**[[Chacoura River]]\n**[[Sacacomie River]]\n**[[Rivi\u00e8re des \u00celes (Rivi\u00e8re du Loup)|Rivi\u00e8re des \u00celes]]\n***[[Sans Bout River]]\n**[[Eau Claire River (Rivi\u00e8re du Loup)|Eau Claire River]]\n**[[Roi River]]\n*[[Little Yamachiche River]]\n*[[Yamachiche River]]\n**[[Machiche River]]\n***[[Rivi\u00e8re du Lac des \u00celes]]\n***[[Rivi\u00e8re du Sept]]\n***[[Bras du Nord (Machiche River tributary)]]/Petite rivi\u00e8re Saint-\u00c9tienne\n*[[Rivi\u00e8re aux Sables (Pointe-du-Lac)|Rivi\u00e8re aux Sables]]\n}}\n\n===Watershed of Saint-Maurice River===\nRivers flowing into the [[Saint Lawrence River]] and [[Gulf of Saint Lawrence]], listed in downstream order:\n\n'''West bank'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*[[Saint-Maurice River]]\n**[[Cypr\u00e8s River]]\n**[[Najoua River]]\n**[[Manouane River (La Tuque)]]\n***[[Ruban River]]\n****[[Blanche River (La Tuque River tributary)]]\n*****[[North-West Blanche River (Ruban River tributary)]]\n****[[Huot River]]\n****[[Pichoui River]]\n*****[[Pichoui River West]]\n****[[Drouin River]]\n***[[La Tuque Creek (Manouane River)]]\n***[[Ca