e River]]\n** [[Le Bras (Ferr\u00e9e River tributary)|Le Bras]]\n** [[Joncas River (Ferr\u00e9e River tributary)|Joncas River]]\n**[[Rouget River]]\n* [[Saint-Jean River (La Pocati\u00e8re)|Saint-Jean River]]\n* [[Ouelle River]]\n** [[Damn\u00e9e River]]\n** [[La Grande Rivi\u00e8re (Ouelle River tributary)|La Grande Rivi\u00e8re]]\n*** [[Chaude River (La Grande Rivi\u00e8re)|Chaude River]]\n*** [[Sainte-Anne River (La Grande Rivi\u00e8re)|Sainte-Anne River]]\n*** [[Rat Musqu\u00e9 River]]\n** [[Bras de la rivi\u00e8re Ouelle]]\n* [[Kamouraska River]] (ex-rivi\u00e8re aux Perles)\n** [[Dufour River]]\n** [[Saint-Denis River (Kamouraska River tributary)|Saint-Denis River]]\n*** [[Bouteillerie River]]\n*** [[Bras de la Rivi\u00e8re Saint-Denis]]\n** [[Goudron River]]\n* [[Fouquette River]]\n* [[Caps River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Rivi\u00e8re du Loup and Eastern tributaries ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Rivi\u00e8re du Loup (Bas-Saint-Laurent)|Rivi\u00e8re du Loup]]\n** [[Pivard River]]\n** [[Le Grand Bras (rivi\u00e8re du Loup)|Le Grand Bras]]\n** [[Manie River]]\n** [[Loutres River (rivi\u00e8re du Loup)|Loutres River]]\n** [[Fourchue River]]\n*** [[Carrier River]]\n*** [[Rocheuse River (lake Morin)|Rocheuse River]]\n**** [[Noire River (Rocheuse River tributary)|Noire River]]\n** [[Little Black River (rivi\u00e8re du Loup)|Little Black River]]\n** [[Little River du Loup (Saint-Antonin)|Little River du Loup]]\n** [[Little River du Loup (rivi\u00e8re-du-Loup)|Little River du Loup]]\n* [[Vases River (L'Isle-Verte)|Vases River]]\n* [[Verte River (rivi\u00e8re-du-Loup)|Verte River]]\n** [[Roches River (Verte River tributary)|Roches River]]\n** [[Cacouna River]]\n** [[Fourche River (Verte River tributary)|Fourche River]]\n* [[Girard River]]\n* [[Petit Sault River]]\n* [[Pointe \u00e0 la Loupe River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Trois-Pistoles River and Eastern tributaries ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Trois Pistoles River]]\n** [[Gamelle River]]\n** [[Plainasse River]]\n** [[Mariak\u00e8che River]]\n*** [[Chaud Stream (Mariak\u00e8che River tributary)|Chaud Stream]]\n** [[S\u00e9nescoup\u00e9 River]]\n*** [[Lake of Grande Fourche]]\n**** [[Saint-Hubert River]]\n** [[Toupik\u00e9 River]]\n*** [[Plate River (Rimouski-Neigette)|Plate River]]\n** [[Boisbouscache River]]\n*** [[Sapins River (Boisbouscache River tributary)|Sapins River]]\n**** [[Ferr\u00e9e River (Sapins River tributary)|Ferr\u00e9e River]]\n*** [[Bouleaux River (Boisbouscache River tributary)|Bouleaux River]]\n*** [[Perdrix River (Boisbouscache River tributary)|Perdrix River]]\n*** [[La Franchise River]]\n*** [[Abraham-Bell River]]\n*** [[Abraham River (Boisbouscache River tributary)|Abraham River]]\n** [[Sauvagesse River]]\n* [[Renouf River]]\n** [[Desch\u00eanes River]]\n* [[Harton River]]\n* [[Centrale River]]\n** [[Little River North of Mountain]]\n* [[Porc-Pic River]]\n* [[River South-West]]\n** [[Neigette River (Les Basques)|Neigette River]]\n* [[Bic River]]\n** [[Aulnes River (Bic River tributary)|Aulnes River]]\n** [[Gamache River (Rimouski-Neigette)|Gamache River]]\n* [[H\u00e2t\u00e9e River]]\n** [[Branche de la rivi\u00e8re H\u00e2t\u00e9e]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Rimouski River and Eastern tributaries ===\n* [[Rimouski River]]\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n'''West bank''' (from confluence)\n* [[Rigoumabe River]]\n* [[Little Rimouski River]]\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re des Accores]]\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re Plate (petite Rivi\u00e8re Rimouski)|Rivi\u00e8re Plate]] (Flat River (Little Rimouski River))\n* [[Noire River (Rimouski River tributary)|Noire River]]\n* [[Blanche River (Rimouski River tributary)|Blanche River]]\n* [[Little Touradi River]]\n* [[France River]]\n* [[Boucher River (Rimouski River tributary)|Boucher River]]\n* [[Grand Touradi River]]\n** [[Brisson River (Grand Touradi River tributary)|Brisson River]]\n** [[Cennelier River]]\n\n'''East bank''' (from upper part)\n* [[Br\u00fbl\u00e9 River]]\n* [[Bois Br\u00fbl\u00e9 River]]\n* [[Macp\u00e